[
  {
    "startTime": 14.5,
    "endTime": 15.9,
    "text": "Buzz Lightyear to Star Command."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.9,
    "endTime": 18.5,
    "text": "Come in, Star Command."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.5,
    "endTime": 19.9,
    "text": "Star Command, come in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.9,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Do you read me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 23.2,
    "text": "Why don't they answer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.2,
    "endTime": 27.2,
    "text": "My ship!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.2,
    "endTime": 30.8,
    "text": "Blast. This will take weeks to repair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.8,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "Buzz Lightyear mission log, stardate 4-0-7-2."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 37.2,
    "text": "My ship has run off course en route to Sector 12."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.2,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "I've crash-landed on a strange planet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 44.7,
    "text": "The impact must have awoke me from hypersleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.7,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "Terrain seems a bit unstable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 50.3,
    "text": "No readout yet if the air is breathable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.3,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "And there seems to be no sign of intelligent life anywhere.- Hello?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 58.2,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.2,
    "endTime": 60.400000000000006,
    "text": "Did I frighten you? Didn't mean to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.4,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "Sorry. Howdy. My name is Woody, and this is Andy's room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 66.9,
    "text": "That's all I wanted to say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.9,
    "endTime": 72.2,
    "text": "And also, there has been a bit of a mix-up. This is my spot, see, the bed here..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.3,
    "endTime": 74.5,
    "text": "Local law enforcement. It's about time you got here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.5,
    "endTime": 77.6,
    "text": "I'm Buzz Lightyear. Space Ranger Universe Protection Unit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.6,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "My ship has crash-landed here by mistake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 83.9,
    "text": "Yes, it is a mistake, because you see, the bed here is my spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.9,
    "endTime": 88.5,
    "text": "I need to repair my turbo boosters. Do people still use fossil fuels, or have you discovered crystallic fusion?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.5,
    "endTime": 91.2,
    "text": "Well, let's see. We got double A's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.2,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "Watch yourself. Halt! Who goes there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Don't shoot. It's okay. Friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Do you know these life-forms?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 99.5,
    "text": "Yes. They're Andy's toys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.5,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "All right, everyone, you're clear to come up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 104.6,
    "text": "I am Buzz Lightyear. I come in peace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.6,
    "endTime": 109.19999999999999,
    "text": "Oh, I'm so glad you're not a dinosaur."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.3,
    "endTime": 110.3,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.3,
    "endTime": 113.39999999999999,
    "text": "Now, thank you all for your kind welcome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.4,
    "endTime": 115.4,
    "text": "Say, what's that button do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.4,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "I'll show you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 119.3,
    "text": "Buzz Lightyear to the rescue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.3,
    "endTime": 120.8,
    "text": "Hey, Woody's got something like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.8,
    "endTime": 124.39999999999999,
    "text": "His is a pull stripe. Only it's... - Only it sounds like a car ran over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.4,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, but not like this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "This is a quality sound system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 129.7,
    "text": "Probably all copper wiring, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.7,
    "endTime": 131.39999999999998,
    "text": "So, where are you from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.4,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "Singapore? Hong Kong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 137.4,
    "text": "Well, no. Actually, I'm stationed up in the Gamma Quadrant of Sector 4."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.7,
    "endTime": 149.39999999999998,
    "text": "As a member of the elite Universe Protection Unit of the Space Ranger Corps, I protect the galaxy from the threat of invasion from the evil Emperor Zurg, sworn enemy of the Galactic Alliance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.4,
    "endTime": 150.4,
    "text": "Oh, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.4,
    "endTime": 151.3,
    "text": "I'm from Playskool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.3,
    "endTime": 152.60000000000002,
    "text": "And I'm from Mattel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.6,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Well, I'm not really from Mattel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 157.4,
    "text": "I'm actually from a smaller company that was purchased in a leveraged buyout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.4,
    "endTime": 157.70000000000002,
    "text": "Well, I don't..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.8,
    "endTime": 159.9,
    "text": "You think they've never seen a new toy before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.7,
    "endTime": 161.39999999999998,
    "text": "Well, sure. Look at him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.4,
    "endTime": 165.3,
    "text": "He's got more gadgets on him than a Swiss Army knife."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.3,
    "endTime": 166.70000000000002,
    "text": "Ah, ah, ah, ah. Please be careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.9,
    "endTime": 168.70000000000002,
    "text": "You don't want to be in the way when my laser goes off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.7,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "Hey, a laser?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 172.3,
    "text": "How come you don't have a laser, Woody?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.3,
    "endTime": 173.70000000000002,
    "text": "It's not a laser."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.7,
    "endTime": 175.29999999999998,
    "text": "It's a little light bulb that blinks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.3,
    "endTime": 175.9,
    "text": "What's with him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.9,
    "endTime": 176.8,
    "text": "Laser envy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "All right, that's enough. Look, we're all very impressed with Andy's new toy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 182.3,
    "text": "Toy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.4,
    "endTime": 184.4,
    "text": "T-O-Y. Toy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.4,
    "endTime": 188.3,
    "text": "Excuse me. I think the word you're searching for is \"Space Ranger.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.4,
    "endTime": 193.0,
    "text": "The word I'm searching for I can't say because there's preschool toys present."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 194.6,
    "text": "Getting' kinda tense, aren't ya?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.7,
    "endTime": 197.2,
    "text": "Uh, Mr. Lightyear. Now, I'm curious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.4,
    "endTime": 200.4,
    "text": "What does a Space Ranger actually do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.4,
    "endTime": 202.3,
    "text": "He's not a Space Ranger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.3,
    "endTime": 206.3,
    "text": "He doesn't fight evil or shoot lasers or fly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.3,
    "endTime": 209.8,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.8,
    "endTime": 211.70000000000002,
    "text": "Oh, impressive wingspan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.7,
    "endTime": 212.39999999999998,
    "text": "Very good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.4,
    "endTime": 213.4,
    "text": "Oh, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.4,
    "endTime": 214.3,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.3,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "These are plastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.0,
    "endTime": 217.1,
    "text": "He can't fly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.1,
    "endTime": 222.7,
    "text": "They are a teryllium carbonic alloy, and I can fly. - No, you can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.7,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "Yes, I can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 224.6,
    "text": "You can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.6,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "Can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 226.9,
    "text": "Can't. Can't. Can't!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.9,
    "endTime": 229.3,
    "text": "I tell you, I could fly around this room with my eyes closed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.4,
    "endTime": 231.70000000000002,
    "text": "Okay, then, Mr. Light Beer, prove it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.7,
    "endTime": 233.79999999999998,
    "text": "All right, then I will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.8,
    "endTime": 243.10000000000002,
    "text": "Stand back, everyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.3,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "To infinity and beyond!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.9,
    "endTime": 273.9,
    "text": "Can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.9,
    "endTime": 275.2,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.2,
    "endTime": 278.4,
    "text": "Oh, wow. You flew magnificently!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.4,
    "endTime": 280.0,
    "text": "I found my movin' buddy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.0,
    "endTime": 281.0,
    "text": "All right, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.0,
    "endTime": 282.3,
    "text": "Thank, thank you all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.3,
    "endTime": 282.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.5,
    "endTime": 284.1,
    "text": "That wasn't flying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.1,
    "endTime": 286.6,
    "text": "That was falling with style."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.6,
    "endTime": 290.6,
    "text": "Man, the dolls must really go for you. Can you teach me that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.7,
    "endTime": 292.2,
    "text": "Golly bob howdy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.2,
    "endTime": 293.9,
    "text": "Oh, shut up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.9,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "You know, in a couple of days, everything will be just the way it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.1,
    "endTime": 298.5,
    "text": "They'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.6,
    "endTime": 299.1,
    "text": "They'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.2,
    "endTime": 302.0,
    "text": "I'm still Andy's favorite toy."
  }
]